reviewText: Cute book, getting my daughter interested in being a big sister (has 4 months to go, so we wanted to prep her).  This book is geared for a toddler who already is a big sister.  I've ordered another one that talks about the baby coming.
title: I'm a Big Sister

reviewText: Bought it for my 2 1/2 year old, she liked the pictures and it has a simple story. Better than other book I've seen.
title: I'm a Big Sister
